{"tid":2394014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務院重申中國在新疆犯下種族滅絕罪行 有關集體大規模強姦 性虐待事件令人震驚 必須嚴懲相關人士","createTime":"2021-02-04T01:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T13:05:23.000Z","uid":292499,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"514113866f4b18e5b416b4da6f3b0257c6cd5004","tid":2394014,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:49:51.000Z","msg":"BBC 的報道引述數名曾被關在「再教育營」的女性及一名守衛指，曾經歷或見過有組織的大規模強姦，性虐待和酷刑。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人被問到相關報道時表示，美國對拘禁維吾爾及穆斯林的新疆集中營發生的暴行深感不安，包括當中的大規模系統性強姦和性虐待的第一手證詞。發言人重申，中國在新疆犯下種族滅絕、侵犯人類的罪行，如斯暴行令有良心的人感到震驚，必須嚴懲。又表示，中國應立即讓獨立調查員及國際觀察家調查在新疆發生的種種罪行。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/美國務院-新疆集中營集體性侵性虐事件令人震驚-必須嚴懲/?fbclid=IwAR2QIdYAl9xblftr9vv92GwaN3Kg1ZXiYglhD4vqxwuLkPmxqooCdkrwtPE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%87%9F%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E6%80%A7%E8%99%90%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%87%E9%A9%9A-%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E5%9A%B4%E6%87%B2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2QIdYAl9xblftr9vv92GwaN3Kg1ZXiYglhD4vqxwuLkPmxqooCdkrwtPE&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=8c6001b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%87%9F%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E6%80%A7%E8%99%90%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%87%E9%A9%9A-%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E5%9A%B4%E6%87%B2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2QIdYAl9xblftr9vv92GwaN3Kg1ZXiYglhD4vqxwuLkPmxqooCdkrwtPE&h=9509b071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/美國務院-新疆集中營集體性侵性虐事件令人震驚-必須嚴懲/?fbclid=IwAR2QIdYAl9xblftr9vv92GwaN3Kg1ZXiYglhD4vqxwuLkPmxqooCdkrwtPE</a>"},{"pid":"fd6b2c1745b423d242e74bf9a7a798544992780d","tid":2394014,"uid":292499,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01